<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>UniConnect — Feed</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css"/>
  <!-- Tailwind required for footer -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/tailwind.css"/>
  <style>
    /* ── Topbar ── */

    /* ── Main content ── */
    .main {
      margin-right: 260px; /* right sidebar width */
      padding: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    /* Constrain feed to a readable fixed width */
    .feed-column {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 620px;
    }

    .page-header { margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }

    /* ── Create Post Box ── */
    .create-post {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(13,27,42,0.07);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .create-post-top {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .create-post-avatar {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--navy);
      font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.8rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      border: 2px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .create-post-input-wrap {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--cream);
      transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding-right: 0.25rem;
    }
    .create-post-input-wrap:focus-within {
      border-color: var(--navy-light);
      background: #fff;
    }

    .create-post-input {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
      border: none;
      background: transparent;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      outline: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .create-post-input:focus { cursor: text; }
    .create-post-input::placeholder { color: #b0b8c4; }

    .create-post-attach {
      width: 32px; height: 32px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: none;
      background: transparent;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      cursor: pointer;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
    }
    .create-post-attach:hover {
      background: var(--cream-dark);
      color: var(--navy);
    }

    /* ── Right Sidebar ── */
    .right-sidebar {
      position: fixed; top: var(--topbar-h); right: 0; bottom: 0;
      width: 260px;
      background: #fff; border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem; overflow-y: auto; z-index: 90;
    }

    .right-sidebar-section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }

    .right-sidebar-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .right-sidebar-item {
      display: block;
      padding: 0.45rem 0;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }
    .right-sidebar-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .right-sidebar-item:hover { color: var(--navy); }

    /* ── Post Card (from post.html) ── */
    .post-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(13,27,42,0.07);
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .post-actions {
      position: absolute;
      top: 1.25rem;
      right: 1.25rem;
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .post-action-btn {
      width: 34px; height: 34px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--cream);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
    }
    .post-action-btn:hover {
      background: var(--cream-dark);
      color: var(--navy);
    }

    .post-author {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      padding-right: 8rem;
    }

    .post-avatar {
      width: 56px; height: 56px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: var(--cream-dark);
    }

    .post-avatar-initials {
      width: 56px; height: 56px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--gold);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .post-author-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.15rem; }

    .post-author-name { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-dark); }
    .post-author-name a { color: var(--text-dark); text-decoration: none; }
    .post-author-name a:hover { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }

    .post-meta { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .post-meta a { color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; }
    .post-meta a:hover { color: var(--navy); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }

    .post-community { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--navy); font-weight: 500; }
    .post-community a { color: var(--navy); text-decoration: none; }
    .post-community a:hover { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }

    .post-body {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.65rem;
      font-size: 0.93rem;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('header', { initials: 'JB' }) %>

  <div class="layout">

    <!-- Left Sidebar -->
    <%- include('sidebar', { activePage: 'feed' }) %>

    <!-- Feed -->
    <main class="main">
      <div class="feed-column">

      <div class="page-header">
        <h1 class="page-title">Feed</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">Recent posts from your courses and communities.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Create Post -->
      <div class="create-post">
        <div class="create-post-top">
          <div class="create-post-avatar">JS</div>
          <div class="create-post-input-wrap">
            <input class="create-post-input" type="text" placeholder="What's on your mind?"/>
            <button class="create-post-attach" title="Attach media">📎</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Post 1 -->
      <div class="post-card">
        <div class="post-actions">
          <button class="post-action-btn" title="Like">👍</button>
          <button class="post-action-btn" title="Comment">💬</button>
          <button class="post-action-btn" title="Bookmark">🔖</button>
        </div>
        <div class="post-author">
          <div class="post-avatar-initials">JB</div>
          <div class="post-author-info">
            <span class="post-author-name"><a href="/profile">Jaden Bryant</a></span>
            <span class="post-meta"><a href="/post">March 6, 2026 at 9:14 AM</a></span>
            <span class="post-community"><a href="/courses">Software Engineering</a></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="post-body">
          <p>Does anyone have notes from Tuesday's lecture on REST API design? I had to leave early and missed the last 20 minutes.</p>
          <p>Specifically looking for the part where Prof. Henderson talked about versioning strategies — I think it was either URI-based or header-based but I'm not sure which he recommended.</p>
          <p>Would really appreciate it, midterm is next week and I want to make sure I have everything covered!</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Post 2 -->
      <div class="post-card">
        <div class="post-actions">
          <button class="post-action-btn" title="Like">👍</button>
          <button class="post-action-btn" title="Comment">💬</button>
          <button class="post-action-btn" title="Bookmark">🔖</button>
        </div>
        <div class="post-author">
          <div class="post-avatar-initials">JS</div>
          <div class="post-author-info">
            <span class="post-author-name"><a href="/profile">Julia Smith</a></span>
            <span class="post-meta"><a href="/post">March 6, 2026 at 8:45 AM</a></span>
            <span class="post-community"><a href="/courses">Data Structures &amp; Algorithms</a></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="post-body">
          <p>Reminder that the study group for the graph algorithms unit is meeting tonight at 7 PM in the library, room 204.</p>
          <p>We'll be going through Dijkstra's and Bellman-Ford — bring your notes and any practice problems you've been stuck on.</p>
          <p>There's space for a few more people if anyone wants to join. Just reply here or message me directly!</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Post 3 -->
      <div class="post-card">
        <div class="post-actions">
          <button class="post-action-btn" title="Like">👍</button>
          <button class="post-action-btn" title="Comment">💬</button>
          <button class="post-action-btn" title="Bookmark">🔖</button>
        </div>
        <div class="post-author">
          <div class="post-avatar-initials">LGR</div>
          <div class="post-author-info">
            <span class="post-author-name"><a href="/profile">Luis Garcia Rangel</a></span>
            <span class="post-meta"><a href="/post">March 5, 2026 at 11:30 PM</a></span>
            <span class="post-community"><a href="/community">Computer Science Club</a></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="post-body">
          <p>Just finished my submission for the spring hackathon — super glad that's done. Built a course scheduler that uses a constraint-satisfaction algorithm to avoid time conflicts.</p>
          <p>Ended up being way more complex than I expected once I added support for professor preferences and room capacity limits.</p>
          <p>If anyone wants to collaborate on cleaning it up and maybe open-sourcing it, let me know. Could be a solid portfolio piece for all of us.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      </div><!-- /.feed-column -->
    </main>

    <!-- Right Sidebar -->
    <aside class="right-sidebar">

      <div class="right-sidebar-section">
        <h2 class="right-sidebar-title">Courses</h2>
        <a href="courses.ejs" class="right-sidebar-item">Intro to Computer Science</a>
        <a href="courses.ejs" class="right-sidebar-item">Data Structures &amp; Algorithms</a>
        <a href="courses.ejs" class="right-sidebar-item">Software Engineering</a>
        <a href="courses.ejs" class="right-sidebar-item">Database Systems</a>
        <a href="courses.ejs" class="right-sidebar-item">Web Development</a>
      </div>

      <div class="right-sidebar-section">
        <h2 class="right-sidebar-title">Communities</h2>
        <a href="community.ejs" class="right-sidebar-item">Computer Science Club</a>
        <a href="#" class="right-sidebar-item">Study Groups</a>
        <a href="#" class="right-sidebar-item">Campus Events</a>
      </div>

    </aside>

  </div>

  <%- include('footer', { footerLayout: 'sidebarBoth' }) %>

</body>
</html>
